                    <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                    <p>Contains letters from Myers to general recipients (neighbors, female correspondents), his parents, and other family members. Letters cover Myers' basic training in California in 1943 through his deployment and return home to Cincinnati in 1945. The series also includes a letter from Myers to his parents announcing his wedding plans in 1949.</p>
